%% Figure 3.4 — Activity Diagram: Event Approval Workflow

flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> Login[User logs in]
    Login --> Create[Fill event creation form]
    Create --> Validate{Valid input?}
    Validate -->|No| ShowErr[Show validation errors]
    ShowErr --> Create
    Validate -->|Yes| ConflictCheck[Run conflict detection]
    ConflictCheck --> Save[Save event as PENDING]
    Save --> NotifyApp[Notify approvers in-system]
    ConflictCheck --> HasConflict{Overlap found?}
    HasConflict -->|Yes| LogConflict[Create ConflictLog record]
    LogConflict --> NotifyConflict[Notify approvers of conflict]
    NotifyConflict --> Save
    HasConflict -->|No| Save
    Save --> Review[Approver reviews event]
    Review --> Decision{Approve or Reject?}
    Decision -->|Reject| Reject[Set status REJECTED + reason]
    Reject --> NotifyOrgR[Notify organiser]
    NotifyOrgR --> End([End])
    Decision -->|Approve| ReCheck[Re-run conflict check]
    ReCheck --> Clear{Slot free?}
    Clear -->|No| Block[Block approval — show error]
    Block --> Review
    Clear -->|Yes| Approve[Set status APPROVED]
    Approve --> ResolveLog[Resolve related conflict logs]
    ResolveLog --> NotifyOrgA[Notify organiser]
    NotifyOrgA --> Calendar[Event visible on calendar]
    Calendar --> End
